Race.SpecificTitle: PW- Police Jury -- 3.07 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide Proposition

Summary: 10 year, 3.07 mills property tax for improving and maintaining
the Allen Parish courthouse and jail.
Race.FullText:
Shall the Parish of Allen, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), be authorized to levy a
special tax of three and seven hundredths (3.07) mills (the estimated amount
reasonably expected to be collected from the levy of the tax for one entire year being
$225,304) on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish for a period of ten (10)
years beginning with the year 2009 and ending with the year 2018, for the purpose of
improving and maintaining the Courthouse and Jail of the Parish?
